WEBVTT

00:00:28.685 --> 00:00:30.186
it is toxic

00:00:30.210 --> 00:00:32.137
and it is predatory.

00:00:34.025 --> 00:00:35.354
Now, I'm from Kenya,

00:00:36.656 --> 00:00:39.664
and in Kenya, corruption
takes different forms.

00:00:41.336 --> 00:00:44.013
I want to share the story
of Karura Forest with you.

00:00:45.822 --> 00:00:48.330
This is my hometown of Nairobi.

00:00:48.977 --> 00:00:50.926
I love Nairobi. It's beautiful.

00:00:51.660 --> 00:00:53.974
But it is a city of paradoxes.

00:00:54.792 --> 00:00:57.758
It is at once beautiful

00:00:57.782 --> 00:00:59.066
and challenging.